trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of toolbox items.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCollection"></xref> class using the specified array of toolbox items.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCollection"> </xref> 클래스 지정된 된 도구 상자 항목 배열을 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: An array of type <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref> containing the toolbox items to fill the collection with.
trans-unit.target: 형식의 배열 <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref> 도구 상자 항목 컬렉션을 채울을 포함 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCollection"></xref> class using the specified collection.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCollection"> </xref> 클래스 지정된 된 컬렉션을 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCollection"></xref> to fill the new collection with.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCollection"> </xref> 을 사용 하 여 새 컬렉션을 채웁니다.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the collection contains the specified <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref>.
A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref> to search the collection for.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref> 에 대 한 컬렉션을 검색 합니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the collection contains the specified object; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>컬렉션에 지정된 된 개체 그렇지 않으면 <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to the specified array beginning with the specified destination index.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 된 대상 인덱스로 시작 하는 지정 된 배열에 컬렉션을 복사합니다.

trans-unit.source: The index to begin copying to.
Gets the index of the specified <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref>, if it exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 지정 된 인덱스를 가져옵니다 <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref>컬렉션에 있는 경우.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref> to get the index of in the collection.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref> 컬렉션에서의 인덱스를 가져올 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref> at the specified index.
The index of the object to get or set.
A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref> at each valid index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref> 컬렉션의 유효한 각 인덱스에 있습니다.
